name: B
description: May the stillness guide you in pivoting to face your desires confidently and with grace. You are infinite and if it wasn't for your attention I would cease to exist. Allegedly but, seriously I'm trying to be the most high-larious may this be the love of laughter Thankfully you can appreciate this forever. It will speak to you when you need it too, just to your highest version of your self which only speaks in truths.
